# React Patterns

- Use functional components with named exports
- Props interfaces named `{ComponentName}Props`
- `src/sections/` maps 1:1 to `docs/specs/00N-*.md`
- `src/components/ui/` contains reusable primitives only (Button, Card, Badge)
- `src/components/layout/` contains Header, Footer, Section wrapper

# Structure

```tsx
// Section example
export function HeroSection() {
  const data = profile; // import from src/data/
  return <Section id="hero">...</Section>;
}
```

# Avoid

- Class components
- Inline data arrays in section files
- Default exports on components
